{"tid":2379693,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"等你攬炒（原曲：等你下課）","createTime":"2021-01-25T11:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T14:37:17.000Z","uid":343520,"like":21,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c813eb996b48b4da3ad9f63ae301a7b0286d0723","tid":2379693,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:32:03.000Z","msg":"作詞：迷上拿卡的本領&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;作曲：周杰倫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你住的巷子裡 埋伏了一班黑人<br />\n為了想與你不期而遇<br />\n流亡半年你為什麼<br />\n為什麼不好好倡議<br />\n拿了我錢卻沒做半點事<br />\n<br />\n我看到你眾籌<br />\n二話不說入錢<br />\n當我開始看到倡議時<br />\n至醒覺誰 攬 走 我 錢<br />\n喔 你又說要攬炒<br />\n到底點用啲錢<br />\n能不能告訴我<br />\n<br />\n數著你家中的鈔票send email<br />\n廁所中影相為呃like多諷刺<br />\n記得我燒給你的銀票<br />\n都什麼年代了到現在我還幻想著<br />\n<br />\n總有一天總有一年會攬炒<br />\n誰會默默的相信你的謊言<br />\n也許我不該再相信攬炒<br />\n下一次又眾籌 也代表我已經走遠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">攬炒巴還我血汗錢！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f74a571234746debb673b68032d9ce000af17192","tid":2379693,"uid":364500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"頭香"},{"pid":"c9641bdbe4155ae4c65861256646418a95aa81bc","tid":2379693,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"使唔使作得咁快呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6ae19ce54b95e3fd8545e8c53b39a38553349d","tid":2379693,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"為公義推！"},{"pid":"bba5cd36777bd2d84124d2ac75c5282420d5f26a","tid":2379693,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:33:06.000Z","msg":"你住的狗圈裏 埋伏了一班黑人"},{"pid":"42da78c4a173a35d195587d4c46c41c2d6e950a3","tid":2379693,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fb